'''Shamira Raphaëla''' (yavutse 1982), ni umukinnyi wa filimi wo muri Aruba ukomoka mu buholandi . <ref>https://www.filmfestival.nl/persoon/shamira-raphaela/</ref> Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa documentaire ''Daddy and the Warlord'', ''Deal With It'' and ''Our Motherland''.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1982 muri Karayibe, akurira muri Aruba kwa nyina w’Ubuholandi na se wa Curaçao. <ref name="caribi">https://caribischnetwerk.ntr.nl/2019/10/15/shamira-raphaela-aruba-het-gouden-kalf-komt-naar-huis/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Nyuma ya voorbereidend wetenschappelijk onderwijs (VWO), yimukiye mu Buholandi yiga ubuhanzi bwiza muri Gerrit Rietveld Academie . Nyuma yaje kubona impamyabumenyi yubuhanzi bwitangazamakuru muri kaminuza yubuhanzi ya ArtEZ .  Ku ikubitiro, yatangiye gukora nk'umuyobozi wigenga aho yayoboye ibiganiro byinshi bya tereviziyo: ''Expeditie Robinson'' na ''Spuiten en Slikken'' . <ref name="caribi" />

Muri 2006, Raphaela yakoze kandi ayobora film ye ya mbere ''Yumunyu Mumaso Yanjye'' . Amagambo magufi avuga abakobwa batatu ba Aruban. Nyuma yo gutsinda kwikabutura nyinshi, yakoze bwa mbere documentaire ''Deal With It'' . Iyi filime yakiriwe neza nyuma iza gutangwa mu iserukiramuco rya sinema ry’umujyi wa Los Angeles, iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Belize ndetse n’iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Aruba. Iyi filime irazenguruka inkuru y’abacuruza ibiyobyabwenge n’abasinzi: se Pempy na murumuna we Andy, mubyukuri abo mu muryango we. Iyi filime yatorewe kuba umukinnyi wa mbere witwaye neza mu iserukiramuco rya Filime ry’Ubuholandi (NFF) 2015. Muri 2017, iyi filime yahawe igihembo cya Lenno na Sunfish igihembo mpuzamahanga cy'amafilime mpuzamahanga ya Amsterdam (IDFA) kubera igihembo cyiza cy'urubyiruko.  <ref name="krakowfilmfestival">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.krakowfilmfestival.pl/en/online-cinema/film/?f=3169 "Our Motherland"]. krakowfilmfestival<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">8 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Muri 2017, yanditse filime ''Yamanutse ya Superwoman'' aho yatsindiye igihembo cya Karen de Bok muri IDFA, 2018. Muri uwo mwaka, yakoze ''Lenno na Angelfish'' . Iyi filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana igihembo cy’inyandiko nziza z’abana b’i Burayi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Berlin mu 2019 hanyuma ihabwa igihembo cy’inyandiko nziza z’abana muri IDFA, 2018.  <ref name="krakowfilmfestival">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.krakowfilmfestival.pl/en/online-cinema/film/?f=3169 "Our Motherland"]. krakowfilmfestival<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">8 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Muri 2018, yakoze documentaire yerekana ubuzima bwa ''Daddy na Warlord'' izenguruka ku nkuru y’umunyamakuru Clarice Gargard, wahoze ari umugabo w’iburyo bwa Charles Taylor, wahoze ari perezida wa [[Liberiya]] . Filime yagaragaye bwa mbere muri Sinema Iserukiramuco rya film muri 2019. Nyuma, film yatsindiye Inyana ya Zahabu kubwinyandiko ngufi nziza mu iserukiramuco rya sinema ry’Ubuholandi 2019. Ukuboza 2019, yakoze documentaire ''Ons Motherland'' . <ref>https://www.humanrightsfilmfestivalberlin.de/en/daddy-and-warlord</ref>

